About:

A CFFI interface to the Portmidi MIDI library. Can be used with or
without Common Music. This software is released under the LLGPL
license, see http://www.cliki.net/LLGPL for the text of this
agreement.

Installation:

Installation assumes ASDF, CFFI and Portmidi have been installed.

To load without Common Music:
    (require :asdf)
    (push "/path/to/cffi/" asdf:*central-registry*)
    (push "/path/to/portmidi/" asdf:*central-registry*)
    (asdf:operate 'asdf:load-op :portmidi)

To load in Common Music:
    (use-system :portmidi)

Links:

For information about Portmidi see:
    http://www-2.cs.cmu.edu/~music/portmusic/

For information about CFFI see:
    http://common-lisp.net/project/cffi/

